            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>esta</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ondo</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>emisses</ex></expan> III <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>lena</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ondo</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Honigtopf aus Ton. Inschrift nach dem Brand auf der Schulter des Gefäßes eingeritzt (Graffito) worden. Zur Gewichtsangabe s(emisses) III: lies s(emisses) III (unicae) = 1 dodrans = 9 unciae.</p>
            </div>
